{{Actor| | type = Internal | name = DeHackEd placeholder | class = DoomUnusedStates | game = Doom }}[[Classes]]: <u>DoomUnusedStates</u>
Doom defined the states S_STALAG, S_DEADTORSO, and S_DEADBOTTOM but never actually used them. For compatibility with [[DeHackEd]] patches, they still need to be kept around. This actor serves that purpose.
==== [[DECORATE]] definition ==== ACTOR <u>DoomUnusedStates</u> { States { Label1: SMT2 A -1 Stop Label2: PLAY N -1 Stop PLAY S -1 Stop TNT: // MBF compatibility TNT1 A -1 Loop } }
